---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Check Yourself - Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for Check Yourself - Quick Camera Mirror for macOS."
  ogUrl="https://idlefusion.com/check-yourself/privacy"
>
  <main>
    <section class="section-padding">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-12">Check Yourself &middot; Effective February 13, 2026</p>

        <div class="space-y-8 text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3">The Short Version</h2>
            <p>Check Yourself does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data. Your camera feed stays on your Mac.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3">Camera Access</h2>
            <p>Check Yourself uses your Mac's camera to display a live mirror view. The camera feed is rendered locally and is never recorded, stored, or transmitted. The camera is only active while the popover is open â€” closing the popover stops the camera immediately.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3">Data Storage</h2>
            <p>Check Yourself stores only your zoom preference locally on your device using standard macOS user defaults. No other data is saved.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3">Analytics & Tracking</h2>
            <p>Check Yourself contains no analytics frameworks, no ad SDKs, no tracking pixels, and no telemetry of any kind. We do not use any third-party services that collect data.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3">Network Usage</h2>
            <p>Check Yourself makes no network requests. The app works entirely offline. The only network activity associated with the app is through the Mac App Store for updates.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3">Children's Privacy</h2>
            <p>Check Yourself does not knowingly collect any information from anyone, including children under the age of 13.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3">Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p>If this policy changes, we will update this page with the new effective date. Since Check Yourself collects no data, meaningful changes are unlikely.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
